04 Plot Choropleth

In [70]:
#04.1 Create subset data_to_plot_1
data_to_plot_1 = df_sub[['country', 'world_rank']]
In [50]:
#04.2 Create map data_to_plot_1
map = folium.Map(location = [40, -95], zoom_start = 4)
folium.Choropleth(
    geo_data = country_geo, 
    data = data_to_plot_1,
    columns = ['country', 'world_rank'],
    key_on = 'feature.properties.name',
    fill_color = 'YlOrBr', fill_opacity=0.6, line_opacity=0.1,
    legend_name = "World Rankings").add_to(map)

folium.LayerControl().add_to(map)
map
